<p>With most Limelight-driveTrain alignment systems I find a simple m_differentialdrive.archadedrive(0, tx*0.05); to align the shot is enough. If you wish to have a PIDControler then creating a PIDControler object is possible.</p>
<p>I have pushed a new 2022 example of our limelight library using the New command base model that show just this. <a href="https://github.com/GraniteCityGearheads3244/2022_Command_LimeLight_Sample/tree/main" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">https://github.com/GraniteCityGearheads3244/2022_Command_LimeLight_Sample/tree/main</a></p>","post_number":4,"post_type":1,"posts_count":7,"updated_at":"2022-04-04T01:36:23.891Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":1,"reads":79,"readers_count":78,"score":35.8,"yours":false,"topic_id":407742,"topic_slug":"motionmagic-problem","display_username":"Corey Applegate","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"link_counts":[{"url":"https://github.com/GraniteCityGearheads3244/2022_Command_LimeLight_Sample/tree/main","internal":false,"reflection":false,"clicks":7}],"read":true,"user_title":"","bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[{"id":2,"count":1}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":25454,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"user_custom_fields":{"user_field_4":"#4607 Engineering Mentor, MN CSA"},"post_url":"/t/motionmagic-problem/407742/4","custom_user_title":"#4607 Engineering Mentor, MN CSA","reactions":[{"id":"heart","type":"emoji","count":1}],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":1,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3036292,"name":"Daniel Wenbo","username":"mendax1234","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/mendax1234/{size}/156242_2.png","created_at":"2022-04-04T01:51:46.709Z","cooked":"<p>Just as <a class="mention" href="/u